title: Jean Goldkette & His Orchestra - Victor Recordings (1924-192
description:
JEAN GOLDKETTE & HIS ORCHESTRA - VICTOR RECORDINGS (1924-1928)

Although most of these tracks (all but three) will appear on any comprehensive Bix Beiderbecke collection, I think Jean Goldkette & His Orchestra deserve a torrent of their own.

In leiu of session info which is on the scans and I don't feel like typing out, I offer this enticing quotation attributed to Rex Stewart from the back of the CD...

"We simply could not compete with Jean Goldkette's Victor Recording Orchestra. Their arrangements were too imaginative, their rhythm too strong."

2001 TransAtlantic Radio
